<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #334155; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .container { background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 16px; padding: 32px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); }
        .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 32px; }
        .logo { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; color: #5AAEEF; text-decoration: none; }
        .content { margin-bottom: 32px; }
        .user-info { background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #f1f5f9; margin: 24px 0; }
        .label { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #64748b; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; font-weight: 700; }
        .value { font-size: 1.1rem; color: #1e293b; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; background: #5AAEEF; color: #ffffff !important; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 12px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; text-align: center; transition: background 0.2s; }
        .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 0.85rem; color: #94a3b8; margin-top: 32px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <a href="#" class="logo">StudySprint</a>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2 style="color: #1e293b; margin-top: 0;">Nouvelle demande de réactivation</h2>
            <p>Bonjour,</p>
            <p>Un utilisateur a soumis une demande pour réactiver son compte StudySprint qui était inactif.</p>
            
            <div class="user-info">
                <div class="label">Utilisateur</div>
                <div class="value">{{ user.prenom }} {{ user.nom }}</div>
                
                <div class="label">Email</div>
                <div class="value">{{ user.email }}</div>
                
                <div class="label">Date de la demande</div>
                <div class="value">{{ "now"|date("d/m/Y à H:i") }}</div>
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{ url('admin_reactivations') }}" class="btn">Traiter la demande</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} StudySprint - Console d'administration
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
